{"tid":1738790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！班狗勁陰濕將48改做72！","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:29:34.000Z","uid":21863,"like":25,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":51,"remark":"已收到會員反映本主題內容的真實性有待確定，請各位會員留意。","replies":[{"pid":"acdd03ad2dee26da98e5670f869d82ebea69e6f4","tid":1738790,"uid":21863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pol/tc/Pol-1128.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpol%2Ftc%2FPol-1128.pdf&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8e5bd906\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pol/tc/Pol-1128.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n真係勁撚陰濕，大選前夕搞d咁既野！<br />\n各位手兄記住不受傷不被捕，點投埋個票先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27bb17eadf5d60fc1ebf9126e5f0e6d5b0c7b7a","tid":1738790,"uid":87690,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"Diu push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c19ffe125e8398efb332dbab63affabf65ec53b","tid":1738790,"uid":152585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"481793ad226bbb10522b9103d8a090ae6a872050","tid":1738790,"uid":21863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"甴近平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baefa8d8f711444dcf085ceac1e2cc590360e732","tid":1738790,"uid":28970,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uodmWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uodmWB.png&h=dedbc8d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c3c5dea8266ef5d724a863d82c71d62db51f281","tid":1738790,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1278b9644ad71623cef3963c0f0c1854e49665f0","tid":1738790,"uid":311236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"第115章 《入境條例》<br />\n2A.香港永久性居民享有香港居留權<br />\n(1)香港永久性居民享有香港居留權，換言之，他在不抵觸第2AA(2)條的條文下，具有以下權利 &mdash;&mdash;  (由1997年第124號第3條修訂)<br />\n(a)在香港入境；<br />\n(b)不會被施加任何逗留在香港的條件，而任何向他施加的逗留條件，均屬無效；<br />\n(c)<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不得向他發出遞解離境令</span></strong>；及<br />\n(d)不得向他發出遣送離境令。<br />\n(2)即使有第(1)(c)款的規定，在1987年7月1日之前有遞解離境令向其發出的人，不享有香港居留權，除非該遞解離境令已期滿失效或撤銷。"},{"pid":"e0557c30524c8e00794bef62ce67b598075a13c1","tid":1738790,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"998150640d61fa90e775e9fbed376d7200977574","tid":1738790,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5547229c03b30fb611a347be0d9fc82d7dedda1","tid":1738790,"uid":78222,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遞解出境</span></span>先係72"},{"pid":"c817c4f8923481ab716052707056de29c4c49b95","tid":1738790,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"遞解出境先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdffc29f6b8d6b7d1d8529aeec0ebe23c3044f2d","tid":1738790,"uid":33903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2